Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:31.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被強行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:37.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:42.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:44.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:47.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:52.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:52.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
